body.name: Home 'Citrus' Lemon & Mango Carpet Powder & Upholstery Freshener, Odor Eliminator, Deodorizer For Homes With Kids & Pets

byLineInfo.name: Visit the The Diamond Life Store

features: Environment friendly, sustainable everyday luxe home essentials.
Formulated with 100% natural ingredients with no harsh chemicals.
Great for use on carpets, rugs, mattresses, pet beds, and sofas.
A little goes a long way. Easy to use. Simply shake, let sit for 10 minutes to absorb odors, vacuum, and relish in the aroma.
WARNING: Inspired by Capri Blue. this bright, lemony scent is highly addictive.
body.description: Give your home a spa day with our natural carpet powder. Made with a blend of baking soda and essential oils, this carpet powder effectively removes dirt, odors, and pet stains without the use of harsh chemicals. The combination of baking soda and essential oils not only cleans carpets but also leaves them smelling fresh and natural. Perfect for homes with pets or those who are looking for a safe and natural alternative to traditional carpet cleaners. Features and Benefits: Made with baking soda and essential oils. Safe for homes and pets. Effectively removes dirt, odors, and pet stains. Leaves carpets smelling fresh and natural. Chemical-free alternative to traditional carpet cleaners.

reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Took a while to arrive and basically one time use.
reviews.reviewText: These took 2 weeks to arrive and was a much smaller package than I realized it would be. I used the whole thing, very conservatively, in one sitting. Now. My carpets are plush and my home is 3400sf. I only got to my living room and guest room, about 1000 square feet between these two rooms. The small was very faint. Not great for my purpose. But may be better for someone with a small space and little carpeting. For an actual scent. You’d have to layer on something else.
